HTTP API

    POST /blobs/sha1/$hash
        needs to be limited to specific IP ranges

    GET  /blobs/sha1/$hash
        anybody can retrieve files

cmdline API

    $MOZ_UPLOAD_CMD="upload.py -u http://upload.mozilla.org:1234 --branch mozilla-inbound"


    test code:
        if [ -n "$MOZ_UPLOAD_CMD" ]; then
            $MOZ_UPLOAD_CMD screenshot.png
        fi

        outputs:
            screenshot.png http://upload.mozilla.org:1234/blobs/sha1/asdfasfadsf
            stackdumpdmp   http://upload.mozilla.org:1234/blobs/sha1/2134q3249


metadata spec
    filename
    filesize
    branch
    mimetype
    upload time
    uploaded by ipLKJASDFLKJlasdflaskdjfasfd
